{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":579681,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那我可以用会遭到网络暴力为理由拒绝实名道歉吗","timestamp":1605788508,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579688,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"骂两句我会停下来，别人不保证，这件事也给我提了个醒-远离是非之地，强势保护自己","timestamp":1605788559,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579696,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我觉得如果女生真的实名而诚恳地道歉了，那再网络暴力她的人反而会成为众矢之的","timestamp":1605788621,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579698,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我肯定不会再继续管这件事了","timestamp":1605788632,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579706,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 问题在于身份很难藏住，实名道歉是试图消解网络暴力的唯一方法。","timestamp":1605788672,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579749,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"感觉这个事无解，对于想网暴的人（暂且这么说吧），不存在无可挑剔的道歉这个说法，事情会像滚雪球一样越闹越大（有了一个实名的人，说不定接下来就有人深扒黑料）。毕竟现在匿名，由着心情发言的人太多了，各种骂战、阴阳。。。Alice表示看累了。","timestamp":1605788879,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579753,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 不好意思，是eve","timestamp":1605788904,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579848,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"所以就不道歉了，懂了","timestamp":1605789348,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579929,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我们并不能代表她本人的思想，也不是什么懂不懂的问题，大的网络环境如此。只能看她本人愿不愿意承受这样的后果（后果已经很清楚了）","timestamp":1605789908,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579991,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 她愿不愿意承受和会不会承受，完全不是一回事","timestamp":1605790451,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":580027,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"必然会 dz你看看树洞有多少人对这位女生的侮辱指责是出于吃瓜找乐子呢 网暴永远是错的 一群加害者指责一个加害者罢了","timestamp":1605790773,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":580466,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":120704,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"就她那德行，她会公开道歉？就算是那也是假巴意思哈哈哈谁还会信这么一个烂人","timestamp":1605793030,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":120704,"reply":12,"tag":null,"text":"#120699 \n那么就有一个很有趣的问题：\n如果女生主动曝光了身份，并进行了至少形式上无可挑剔的抱歉等行为，现在树洞上对她进行批评的人，之后还会对她进行“网络暴力”吗","timestamp":1605788463,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782651,"url":"","vote":{}}}